  "pinData": {},
  "notes": "## Proaktive Zahlungserinnerung (3 Tage vor Fälligkeit)\n\n### Purpose\nSends a friendly payment reminder email 3 days BEFORE an invoice is due.\nThis is a pre-dunning step to reduce the number of overdue invoices.\n\n### Flow\n1. Cron trigger: Daily at 08:00 Europe/Berlin\n2. Fetch all open invoices from Supabase (status='offen')\n3. Calculate due_date = created_at + zahlungsziel_tage\n4. Filter: only invoices due exactly 3 days from now AND with customer email\n5. Send friendly reminder via FreyAI email relay (freyavision-email container)\n6. Log to automation_log\n\n### Dependencies\n- SUPABASE_URL + SUPABASE_KEY env vars in n8n\n- EMAIL_RELAY_SECRET env var in n8n\n- freyavision-email container running on host network (port 3100)\n- Supabase credential 'Supabase API' configured in n8n\n\n### Email Content\nGerman professional tone: 'Freundliche Erinnerung: Ihre Rechnung [Nr] über [Betrag] EUR wird in 3 Tagen fällig.'"
}
